\lim_{n\to\infty}{\frac{F_{n+1}}{F_n}} = L
L = \lim_{n\to\infty}{\frac{F_{n+1}}{F_{n}}} = \lim_{n\to\infty}{\frac{F_{n}}{F_{n-1}}}
L = \lim_{n\to\infty}{\frac{F_{n} + F_{n-1}}{F_{n}}} = \lim_{n\to\infty}{\frac{F_{n}}{F_{n-1}}}
L =\lim_{n\to\infty}{1 + \frac{ F_{n-1}}{F_{n}}} = 1 + \lim_{n\to\infty}{\frac{ F_{n-1}}{F_{n}}} = \lim_{n\to\infty}{\frac{F_{n}}{F_{n-1}}}
